n-nullish value\", you probably want `NonNullable<unknown>` instead.","TSTypeLiteral","bannedTypeMessage",["1403","1404","1405","1406"],["1407"],["1408","1409","1410","1411"],["1412"],"react-perf/jsx-no-new-object-as-prop","JSX attribute values should not contain objects created in the same scope","ObjectExpression","@typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any","Unexpected any. Specify a different type.","TSAnyKeyword","unexpectedAny",["1413","1414"],["1415"],"react-perf/jsx-no-jsx-as-prop","JSX attribute values should not contain other JSX","JSXElement","react-hooks/exhaustive-deps","React Hook useCallback has an unnecessary dependency: 'state.collection'. Either exclude it or remove the dependency array.","ArrayExpression",["1416"],"react-perf/jsx-no-new-array-as-prop","JSX attribute values should not contain Arrays created in the same scope",["1417"],["1418"],["1419"],"@appsmith/named-use-effect","The function inside the useEffect should be named for better readability eg: useEffect(function mySideEffect() {...}, [])","useNamedUseEffect",["1420"],["1421"],["1422"],"React Hook useCallback has an unnecessary dependency: 'inputRef.current'. Either exclude it or remove the dependency array. Mutable values like 'inputRef.current' aren't valid dependencies because mutating them doesn't re-render the component.",["1423"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'onHeightChange'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["1424"],["1425"],["1426"],["1427"],["1428"],["1429"],["1430"],"React Hook useCallback has an unnecessary dependency: 'props.optionsLabelPosition'. Either exclude it or remove the dependency array.",["1431"],["1432","1433"],["1434"],["1435","1436"],["1437"],{"kind":"1438","justification":"1439"},{"kind":"1438","justification":"1439"},{"kind":"1438","justification":"1439"},{"kind":"1438","justification":"1439"},{"kind":"1438","justification":"1439"},{"messageId":"1440","data":"1441","fix":"1442","desc":"1443"},{"messageId":"1440","data":"1444","fix